data.description: Gated in Sunterra Crystal Lagoon!!! Welcome to the epitome of luxury living in Sunterra Crystal Lagoon! This 2-story haven boasts 4 bedrooms, a study room, and 2.5 baths, providing ample space for your family's comfort. Nestled in the acclaimed Katy ISD, rest assured your children receive top-tier education.    Enjoy the convenience of being minutes away from Katy Asian Town, Katy Mills shopping mall, Typhoon Texas Water Park, and major retailers like Costco, Walmart, HEB, and Kroger. Immerse yourself in the perfect blend of sophistication and convenience. Your dream home awaits in the vibrant heart of Sunterra Crystal Lagoon – seize this opportunity to live the lifestyle you deserve!
